Package hac.classes.forGame

Class UpdateObject

java.lang.Object
hac.classes.forGame.UpdateObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class UpdateObject extends Object implements Serializable
An update object includes maps for the update array in room. It looks like that: {attackDetails:{attackerName:___, opponentName:___, row:___, col:___}, boardChanges:[{row:___, col:___, status:"Hit"/"Miss"}, {..}, ...]}, ...] Rows and columns need to be 0 <= integer < Board.Size. attackerName is the username of the attacker, opponentName is the attacked player's username.
